- [ ] Batch operations implemented where needed
- [ ] Search/filter endpoints functional
- [ ] Pagination implemented on list endpoints
- [ ] File upload endpoints functional (if applicable)
- [ ] Webhook endpoints configured (if applicable)

### 3.2 Route Validation
- [ ] All frontend routes defined and accessible
- [ ] Protected routes have authentication checks
- [ ] 404/catch-all routes implemented
- [ ] Deep linking functional for all routes
- [ ] Route parameters properly typed and validated
- [ ] Query parameters handled correctly
- [ ] Redirect logic functional and tested

### 3.3 API Documentation
- [ ] OpenAPI/Swagger documentation complete
- [ ] All endpoints documented with examples
- [ ] Request/response schemas defined
